object.customQuery:
SELECT coalesce( c.Policy_Symbol+c.Policy_Number+c.Module_Number +c.Company_Number, b.POLICY_KEY
,'NA') as Policy_Key
,coalesce( c.claim_key, -1) as Claim_Key
,
stg.PolicySymbol, stg.PolicyNumber, stg.CompanyNumber, stg.ClaimNumber, stg.LossDate, stg.RiskState, stg.MajorPerilId, stg.Stateline, 
stg.AnnualStatementLine, stg.LossPaidAmount, stg.LossExpenseAmount, stg.CededReinCompany, stg.Agent, 
stg.AccountDate, stg.LineOfBusiness, stg.Transactions, stg.PolicyEffectiveDate, stg.PolicyExpirationDate 
FROM
 dbo.Ceded_LossReinsurance_Stg  stg
 left join dbo.lkp_claim_key c
on c.claim_number=stg.claimnumber
and stg.policynumber=c.policy_number
and stg.policysymbol=c.policy_symbol
left join  (
select Policy_number,policy_symbol,max(Policy_Key) as policy_key from dbo.lkp_policy_key group by Policy_number,policy_symbol)b
on stg.policysymbol=b.policy_symbol
and stg.policynumber=b.policy_number
where  agent='0019'
